Take aways
Monopoly stocks to avoid 
1. PSU stocks (Public Sector Enterprises)
2. The enterprises in which government intervention is high
3. No steady growth or lot of ups and downs enterprises
4. No future plans or no plans in making profits 
Monopoly stocks to buy
1. Company which is interested in making profits 
2. Which has Future growth potential

Recommended stocks to buy
1. Nestle 
2. Pidilite
3. Marico 
4. ITC
